Basic subversion commands as SpaceFm plugin:

update		just updates from remote
commit		commits whole working directory or selected files. Also asks to add unversioned files before comitting
add			adds selected files (command not available if nothing is selected)
diff (PREV)	diffs working directory or selected entry to previous version (tries to use meld or kdiff3 for single selection)
log			log of working directory or selected item  (command not available if more than one entry is selected)
status		status of whole working directory or selected files
